Package com.arjuna.mw.wscf.model.as.coordinator.xa.messages

Class Summary
XACommit The coordinator is committing.
XAEnd The relationship between the coordinator and the participant is ending.
XAForget The participant caused a heuristic and as a result has had to maintain information about it until now.
XAPrepare The coordinator is preparing to commit.
XARecover The transaction is recovering and a list of in doubt resources is being requested.
XARollback The coordinator is rolling back.
XAStart The resource is being (re-) associated with the transaction.
